headline: Reflecting On Professional Tools and Equipment Stocks’ Q2 Earnings: Snap-on (NYSE:SNA)
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Snap-on (NYSE:SNA) and the best and worst performers in the professional tools and equipment industry.
